'''小鹏G3'''是一款由[[小鹏汽车|小鹏汽车]]开发的[[電動汽車|全电动]]{{tsl|en|Compact SUV|紧凑型SUV|}}，由[[海马汽车|海马汽车]]代工生产，最初在2018年发布。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sarkar |first1=Abhijit |title=Xpeng contract out to Haima for production of their G3 SUV |url=http://www.driversmagazine.com/xpeng-contract-haima-production-g3-suv/ |accessdate=2019-05-28 |work=Drivers Magazine |date=2018-02-12 |language=en }}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=【小鹏汽车G3参数配置表】_小鹏汽车_小鹏汽车G3配置_价格单_汽车之家|url=https://car.autohome.com.cn/config/series/4489.html#pvareaid=3454437|work=汽车之家|accessdate=2020-08-24|archive-date=2019-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711155358/https://car.autohome.com.cn/config/series/4489.html#pvareaid=3454437|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 争议 ==
2019年7月10日，小鹏汽车宣布推出G3 2020款。G3 2020款拥有最高520km的综合续航里程，补贴后售价14.38万-19.68万元。上市仅半年的2019款车型综合续航里程最高仅365km，补贴后售价15.58万-19.98万元。旧款车主认为小鹏隐瞒新款上市时间，从而引发不满<ref>{{cite news |author1=罗世浩 |date=2019-07-16 |title=小鹏危机启示录：新能源汽车信任将崩塌？ |url=https://36kr.com/p/5225881 |accessdate=2019-07-24 |work=[[36氪|36氪]] |archive-date=2019-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724150740/https://36kr.com/p/5225881 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=黄珮 |url=https://cj.sina.com.cn/articles/view/2137950223/7f6e880f01900iypf |title=小鹏汽车遭遇信任危机！补救措施能否挽回“鹏友”的心？ |accessdate=2019-07-24 |work=[[人民日报|人民日报]]中国能源报 |archive-date=2019-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724150738/https://cj.sina.com.cn/articles/view/2137950223/7f6e880f01900iypf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有车主到小鹏的总部和门店抗议和维权<ref>{{cite news |author1=魏帅 |title=小鹏汽车口碑崩塌：道歉补偿，车主仍坚持退车退钱 |url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/auto/2019/07/16/604027.html?agt=15422 |accessdate=2019-07-24 |work=[[新京报|新京报]] |date=2019-07-16 |archive-date=2022-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414191418/http://www.bjnews.com.cn/auto/2019/07/16/604027.html?agt=15422 }}</ref>。

